Name: x_team_project
Description: 1 if team t is assigned to project p else 0

Name: y_worker_team
Description: 1 if worker w belongs to team t else 0

Name: sm_team_assignment
Description: 1 if Scrum Master sm supports team t else 0

Name: po_manages_pb
Description: 1 if Product Owner po manages Product Backlog pb else 0

Name: feature_in_pb
Description: 1 if feature f is contained in Product Backlog pb else 0

Name: epic_in_pb
Description: 1 if epic ep is contained in Product Backlog pb else 0

Name: story_in_epic
Description: 1 if user story us is contained in epic ep else 0

Name: task_in_story
Description: 1 if task ts is contained in user story us else 0

Name: story_in_sbl
Description: 1 if user story us is assigned to sprint backlog sbl else 0

Name: sbl_in_sprint
Description: 1 if sprint backlog sbl belongs to sprint sp else 0

Name: task_on_board
Description: 1 if task ts appears on scrum board scb else 0

Name: feature_in_release
Description: 1 if feature f is included in release plan rep else 0

Name: pursue_sp_goal
Description: 1 if sprint sp pursues sprint goal sg else 0
